summary: A slight re-model of Aela\'s face and body, just \'cause I didn\'t like the face in-game and the modded faces provided on this lovely sight.
descriptionHtml:
Did you, like me, take a look at Aela the first time and say to yourself, \"Wow, that\'s a very rectangular face. And dear lord, why is her head so disproportionate with the rest of her body!?\"

Well no more, because I\'ve edited the face to be less rectangular, sharper, and slightly cuter. This is a mod that I made for myself because I wasn\'t completely satisfied with the ones already on the Nexus. I\'m only uploading it for people like me. I also added files that change her voice, but these should only be used if you have completed the Companions story line. TALKING TO HER ABOUT ANY COMPANION QUEST STUFF WITH THE OPTIONAL FILES WILL NOT HAVE ANY AUDIO. Only the basic companion commands will be voiced.
author: BobDylan101
